    "name": "API Testing using Postman",
    "description": "This project demonstrates end-to-end API testing of a User Management system  \ncovering Users, Resources and Authentication modules. Testing includes  \nfunctional validation, negative scenarios, input validation, status code  \nverification and response structure validation.\n\nThe collection validates User Management REST APIs using Postman.\n\nScope:\n\n1.Create User\n\n2.Get User Details\n\n3.Update User\n\n4.Delete User\n\nValidation Includes:\n\n1.Status Code Validation\n\n2.Response body validation\n\n3.Schema validation\n\n4.Negative test cases\n\n5.Automated tests using pm.test\n\nEnvironment Driven Excecution using base_url variable.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "52835001",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/52835001-19f261d8-e00a-4003-90d0-3292eff7d8c0?source=collection_link"
  },
